   <indicator aggregation-status="0" ascending="0" measure="1">
    <title>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">- Improved interest in and knowledge of the Council amongst journalists, especially from developing countries (and especially form Africa); 
- Improved awareness amongst journalists of their role as human rights defenders to hold governments accountable against the State&#x2019;s human rights obligations and commitments;
- Increase in the number and quality of articles/broadcasts focused on the work and output of the Human Rights Council;
